'''心脏出血漏洞'''（{{lang-en|Heartbleed bug}}），简称为'''心血漏洞'''，是一个出现在[[密码学|加密]]程序库[[OpenSSL|OpenSSL]]的[[安全漏洞|安全漏洞]]，该程序库广泛用于实现互联网的[[传输层安全协议|传输层安全]]（TLS）协议。它于2012年被引入了OpenSSL中，2014年4月首次向公众披露。只要使用的是存在缺陷的OpenSSL实例，无论是服务器还是客户端，都可能因此而受到攻击。此问题的原因是在实现TLS的[[心跳_(计算机)|心跳]]扩展时没有对输入进行适当验证（缺少[[边界检查|边界检查]]）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kb.cyberoam.com/default.asp?id=2909|title=Security Advisory – OpenSSL Heartbleed Vulnerability|date=2014-04-11|website=[[Cyberoam|Cyberoam]]|access-date=2018-02-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208124031/https://kb.cyberoam.com/default.asp?id=2909|archivedate=2018-02-08}}</ref>，因此漏洞的名称来源于“心跳”（heartbeat）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gizmodo.com/how-heartbleed-works-the-code-behind-the-internets-se-1561341209|title=How Heartbleed Works: The Code Behind the Internet's Security Nightmare|date=2014-04-09|last1=Limer|first1=Eric|accessdate=2014-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111073625/http://gizmodo.com/how-heartbleed-works-the-code-behind-the-internets-se-1561341209|archivedate=2014-11-11}}</ref>。该程序错误属于[[缓冲区过读|缓冲区过读]]<ref name="cve"/>，即可以读取的数据比应该允许读取的还多<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/126.html|title=CWE-126: Buffer Over-read (3.0)|website=[[Common_Vulnerabilities_and_Exposures|Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures]]|publisher=[[Mitre_Corporation|Mitre]]|date=2018-01-18|language=en|access-date=2018-02-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208124312/https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/126.html|archivedate=2018-02-08}}</ref>。

心脏出血在[[通用漏洞披露|通用漏洞披露]]（CVE）系统中的编号为{{CVE|2014-0160}}<ref name="cve">{{Cite web|url=https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2014-0160|title=CVE-2014-0160|website=[[Common_Vulnerabilities_and_Exposures|Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures]]|publisher=[[Mitre_Corporation|Mitre]]|language=en|access-date=2018-02-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124041203/https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=cve-2014-0160|archivedate=2018-01-24}}</ref>。{{link-en|加拿大网络事故响应中心|Canadian Cyber Incident Response Centre}}发布安全公告，提醒系统管理员注意漏洞<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.publicsafety.gc.ca/cnt/rsrcs/cybr-ctr/2014/al14-005-en.aspx|title=AL14-005: OpenSSL Heartbleed Vulnerability|date=2014-04-11|work=Cyber Security Bulletins|publisher=[[加拿大公共安全部|Public Safety Canada]]|language=en|access-date=2018-02-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208124240/https://www.publicsafety.gc.ca/cnt/rsrcs/cybr-ctr/2014/al14-005-en.aspx|archivedate=2018-02-08}}</ref>。2014年4月7日，即漏洞公开披露的同一天，OpenSSL发布了修复后的版本。

{{As of|2014|05|20}}，在80万最热门的启用TLS的网站中，仍有1.5％易受心脏出血漏洞的攻击。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/05/20/heartbleed_still_prevalent/|title=AVG on Heartbleed: It's dangerous to go alone. Take this (an AVG tool)|last=Leyden|first=John|date=2014-05-20|work=[[The_Register|The Register]]|access-date=2018-02-08|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123214859/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/05/20/heartbleed_still_prevalent/|archivedate=2018-01-23}}</ref>

因为缺陷在于OpenSSL的实现，而不是SSL/TLS协议本身，所以除了OpenSSL之外的其他TLS实现方式，如[[GnuTLS|GnuTLS]]、[[Mozilla基金会|Mozilla]]的[[网络安全服务|网络安全服务]]（NSS）和[[SSPI|Windows平台的TLS实现]]都不受影响<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://cloudblogs.microsoft.com/microsoftsecure/2014/04/10/microsoft-services-unaffected-by-openssl-heartbleed-vulnerability/|title=Microsoft Services unaffected by OpenSSL "Heartbleed" vulnerability|last=Pretorius|first=Tracey|date=2014-04-10|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|access-date=2018-02-08|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208123701/https://cloudblogs.microsoft.com/microsoftsecure/2014/04/10/microsoft-services-unaffected-by-openssl-heartbleed-vulnerability/|archivedate=2018-02-08}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==

2012年2月，传输层安全（TLS）和[[数据报传输层安全|数据报传输层安全]]（DTLS）协议的心跳扩展成为了标准，是为{{IETF RFC|6520}}<ref>{{Cite IETF|title=Transport Layer Security (TLS) and Datagram Transport Layer Security (DTLS) Heartbeat Extension|rfc=6520|last1=Seggelmann|first1=Robin|last2=Tuexen|first2=Michael|last3=Williams|first3=Michael|publisher=[[Internet_Engineering_Task_Force|IETF]]|date=2012-02|access-date=2018-02-08|doi=10.17487/RFC6520|issn=2070-1721}}</ref>。它提供了一种无需每次都重新协商连接，就能测试和保持安全通信链路的方式。2011年，RFC的作者之一，当时[[杜伊斯堡-埃森大学|杜伊斯堡-埃森大学]]的博士生罗宾·赛格尔曼（Robin Seggelmann）为OpenSSL实现了心跳扩展。赛格尔曼向OpenSSL发出的推送请求之后<ref name="smh">{{cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/it-pro/security-it/man-who-introduced-serious-heartbleed-security-flaw-denies-he-inserted-it-deliberately-20140410-zqta1.html |title=Man who introduced serious 'Heartbleed' security flaw denies he inserted it deliberately |date=2014-04-11 |work=[[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |last=Grubb |first=Ben |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412233059/http://www.smh.com.au/it-pro/security-it/man-who-introduced-serious-heartbleed-security-flaw-denies-he-inserted-it-deliberately-20140410-zqta1.html |archivedate=2014-04-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://rt.openssl.org/Ticket/Display.html?user=guest&pass=guest&id=2658 |title=#2658: [PATCH] Add TLS/DTLS Heartbeats |publisher=OpenSSL |year=2011 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808193401/https://rt.openssl.org/Ticket/Display.html?user=guest&pass=guest&id=2658 |archivedate=2017-08-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/meet-the-man-that-created-the-bug-that-almost-broke-the-internet/article17941003/ |title=Meet the man who created the bug that almost broke the Internet |newspaper=Globe and Mail |date=2014-04-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104003820/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/meet-the-man-that-created-the-bug-that-almost-broke-the-internet/article17941003/ |archivedate=2018-01-04 }}</ref>，他的更改由OpenSSL四位核心开发者之一的斯蒂芬·N·汉森（Stephen N. Henson）审核。汉森未能注意到赛格尔曼实现中的错误，于2011年12月31日将有缺陷的代码加入了OpenSSL的源代码库。2012年3月14日，OpenSSL 1.0.1版发布，漏洞开始传播。心跳支持默认是启用的，这使受影响的版本易受攻击<ref name="hb">{{cite web| title = Heartbleed Bug| date = 2014-04-08| url = http://heartbleed.com/| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407203519/http://heartbleed.com/| archivedate = 2014-04-07| accessdate = 2014-04-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| last = Goodin| first = Dan| title = Critical crypto bug in OpenSSL opens two-thirds of the Web to eavesdropping| work = Ars Technica| date = 2014-04-08| url = https://arstechnica.com/security/2014/04/critical-crypto-bug-in-openssl-opens-two-thirds-of-the-web-to-eavesdropping/| deadurl = no| archiveurl = http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20171230112228/https://arstechnica.com/security/2014/04/critical-crypto-bug-in-openssl-opens-two-thirds-of-the-web-to-eavesdropping/| archivedate = 2017-12-30}}</ref><ref name="hbos">{{cite web| title = OpenSSL "Heartbleed" bug: what's at risk on the server and what is not| first = Hagai| last = Bar-El| date = 2014-04-09| url = http://www.hbarel.com/openssl-heartbleed-bug| deadurl = no| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413140412/http://www.hbarel.com/openssl-heartbleed-bug| archivedate = 2014-04-13}}</ref>。

=== 发现 ===
根据OpenSSL的马克·J·考克斯（Mark J. Cox）的说法，谷歌安全团队的尼尔·梅塔（Neel Mehta）于2014年4月1日11:09 UTC报告了心脏出血漏洞<ref>{{cite web |title=Mark J Cox – #Heartbleed |url=https://plus.google.com/+MarkJCox/posts/TmCbp3BhJma |accessdate=2014-04-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416090758/https://plus.google.com/+MarkJCox/posts/TmCbp3BhJma |archivedate=2014-04-16 }}</ref>。

该漏洞由芬兰网络安全公司[[新思科技|Codenomicon]]的工程师命名，该公司也设计了心脏出血标志，并设立了网站{{URL|http://heartbleed.com}}向公众解释该错误<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/style-blog/wp/2014/04/09/why-is-it-called-the-heartbleed-bug/|title=Why is it called the 'Heartbleed Bug'?|last=Dewey|first=Caitlin|accessdate=2014-11-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009063758/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/style-blog/wp/2014/04/09/why-is-it-called-the-heartbleed-bug/|archivedate=2014-10-09}}</ref>。虽然谷歌的安全团队首先向OpenSSL发送了报告，但谷歌和Codenomicon几乎在同一时间分别独立地发现了这个漏洞<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vox.com/cards/heartbleed/who-discovered-the-vulnerability|title=Who discovered the vulnerability?|last=Lee|first=Timothy B.|date=2014-04-10|work=Vox|access-date=2017-12-04|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205093009/https://www.vox.com/cards/heartbleed/who-discovered-the-vulnerability|archivedate=2017-12-05}}</ref><ref name="hb" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://readwrite.com/2014/04/13/heartbleed-security-codenomicon-discovery/|title=How Codenomicon Found The Heartbleed Bug Now Plaguing The Internet - ReadWrite|last=Lee|first=Ariana|date=2014-04-13|work=ReadWrite|access-date=2017-12-04|language=en-US|quote=Discovered independently by Google engineer Neel Mehta and the Finnish security firm Codenomicon, Heartbleed has been called “one of the most serious security problems to ever affect the modern web.”（由谷歌工程师尼尔·梅塔和芬兰安全公司Codenomicon独立发现，心脏出血被称为“影响现代网络的最严重的安全问题之一”。）|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905234021/https://readwrite.com/2014/04/13/heartbleed-security-codenomicon-discovery/|archivedate=2017-09-05}}</ref>。Codenomicon称它于2014年4月3日发现并通知了NCSC-FI以进行漏洞协调<ref name="hb" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Näin suomalaistutkijat löysivät vakavan vuodon internetin sydämestä – transl/Finnish researchers found a serious leakage of the heart of the Internet |url=http://www.digitoday.fi/tietoturva/2014/04/10/nain-suomalaistutkijat-loysivat-vakavan-vuodon-internetin-sydamesta/20145118/66?&n=2#commentsHere |date=2014-04-10 |accessdate=2014-04-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104034647/http://www.digitoday.fi/tietoturva/2014/04/10/nain-suomalaistutkijat-loysivat-vakavan-vuodon-internetin-sydamesta/20145118/66?&n=2#commentsHere |archivedate=2014-11-04 }}</ref>。

